'''悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛'''（{{lang-en|Sydney funnel-web spider}}，[[學名|學名]]：''Atrax robustus''）是[[六疣蛛總科|六疣蛛總科]][[毒疣蛛科|毒疣蛛科]]下的一種[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]，僅發現於[[悉尼|悉尼]]周邊{{convert|100|km|mi}}以內的地區。這是一種毒液有劇毒的蜘蛛，人類被其咬傷後如不及時醫治，便可能有死亡之危。<ref>{{cite web|last=Alcock, MD, MS;|first=Joe|title=Funnel Web Spider Envenomation / Pathophysiology|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/772401-overview#a0104|publisher=Medscape Reference|accessdate=3 November 2012|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226222823/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/772401-overview#a0104|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==命名法==
教士[[奧克塔維厄斯·皮卡德-坎布里奇|奧克塔維厄斯·皮卡德-坎布里奇]]（Octavius Pickard-Cambridge）在1877年發現了一隻雌性的悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛，他也是第一個描述這種生物的人。他給出的學名''Atrax robustus''至今依然沿用。後來[[威廉·約瑟夫·雷恩博|威廉·約瑟夫·雷恩博]]將一隻雄性悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛命名為''Poikilomorpha montana''，但被發現其實是同一物種。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.3853/j.0067-1975.62.2010.1556 |title=A revision of the Australian funnel-web spiders (Hexathelidae: Atracinae) |year=2010 |last1=Gray |first1=Michael R. |journal=Records of the Australian Museum |volume=62 |issue=3 |pages=285}}</ref> 其[[種加詞|種加詞]]來自於[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]“robustus”，意思為“強壯”或“成熟”。<ref name="spiderwatch">{{cite book|last=Brunet|first=Bert|title=Spiderwatch: A Guide to Australian Spiders|publisher=Reed|date=1997|page=91|isbn=0-7301-0486-9}}</ref>

悉尼漏斗蜘蛛是[[澳毒蛛屬|澳毒蛛屬]]下僅有的三個種之一，另外兩個分別是''[[Atrax_sutherlandi|Atrax sutherlandi]]''和''[[Atrax_yorkmainorum|Atrax yorkmainorum]]''。<ref>[[Norman_I._Platnick|Platnick N I]] [http://research.amnh.org/oonopidae/catalog/names.php?genus=Atrax World Spider Catalog] {{Wayback|url=http://research.amnh.org/oonopidae/catalog/names.php?genus=Atrax |date=20120928063014 }} (2008). In 1988, other species were transferred from ''Atrax'' to the genus ''Hadronyche'': ''A. adelaidensis'', ''A. eyrei'', ''A. flindersi'', ''A. formidabilis'', ''A. infensus'', ''A. modestus'','' A. pulvinator'', ''A. validus'','' A. venenatus'' and ''A. versutus''.</ref> 悉尼漏斗蜘蛛的學名與''[[Hadronyche|Hadronyche]]''下的一些種相同。此外，它和'''北部樹棲漏斗網蜘蛛'''（''Hadronyche formidabilis''）是澳洲僅有的兩種咬傷可置人于死地的漏斗網蜘蛛。<ref name=csiro />

==描述==
[[File:Atrax_Robustus.jpg|thumb]]
悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛是一種中大型蜘蛛，體長可達{{convert|1|-|5|cm|in}}。兩性的外表都呈光滑的暗色，色澤本身由黑藍、黑色到褐色不等。覆蓋[[頭胸部|頭胸部]]的甲殼幾乎沒有毛髮。其另外一個特徵是尾部的手指狀[[吐絲器|吐絲器]]。<ref name=museum />

雄性沒有雌性的壽命長，雄性的肢比雌性長。<ref name=csiro>[http://www.csiro.au/resources/Funnelweb-Spider-Facts "Funnel-web spider"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111225005458/http://www.csiro.au/resources/Funnelweb-Spider-Facts |date=2011-12-25 }}, [[CSIRO|CSIRO]], 14.10.2011. Retrieved 18 December 2011.</ref>

==習性==
悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛是陸生蜘蛛，但喜好潮濕的環境。他們會鑄造內部有絲線連接的管狀巢穴，巢穴的洞口則一般會織造漏斗狀的網。<ref name=museum /><ref name=museum2>[http://australianmuseum.net.au/Sydney-Funnel-web-Spider Sydney Funnel-web Spider, Atrax robustus] {{Wayback|url=http://australianmuseum.net.au/Sydney-Funnel-web-Spider |date=20111221225149 }}, ''Australian Museum'', Sydney. Retrieved 18 December 2011.</ref>

雌性更常待在自己的巢穴里，它們的食物包括昆蟲、蜥蜴或者蛙類。當這些動物踏到其洞口的網上時，悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛就會上前將其捕獲并注入毒液。<ref name=museum /><ref name=museum2 /> 雄性一般只在溫暖的季節出沒，尋找合適的雌性進行交配。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.toxicon.2003.11.009 |title=Bites by Australian mygalomorph spiders (Araneae, Mygalomorphae), including funnel-web spiders (Atracinae) and mouse spiders (Actinopodidae: Missulena spp) |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_toxicon_2004-02_43_2/page/133 |year=2004 |last1=Isbister |first1=Geoffrey K |last2=Gray |first2=Mike R |journal=Toxicon |volume=43 |issue=2 |pages=133–40 |pmid=15019472}}</ref> 因此人類與雄性悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛遭遇的機會更大。因為可以將空氣儲存在肢體末端毛髮的氣泡中，悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛可以在水下存活24小時之久。<ref name=museum /> 通常悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛會選擇在夜間出沒，白天環境容易令它們脫水。雨季因為洞穴可能會被湮沒而出現地更加頻繁。<ref name=museum2 />

當遇到威脅時悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛會表現出進攻性行為，它們會用第三對足跳躍起來并露出毒牙。<ref name=museum2 /><ref name=unisydney>[http://www.anaes.med.usyd.edu.au/venom/spiders.html#FUNNELWEB "Australian Spider and Insect Bites"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.anaes.med.usyd.edu.au/venom/spiders.html#FUNNELWEB |date=20120321110650 }}, ''University of Sydney''. Retrieved 18 December 2011.</ref> 它們會緊緊咬住獵物，注入全部毒液并再三襲擊。<ref name=unisydney />

==咬傷==
===毒液===
和其他漏斗網蜘蛛一樣，悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛會分泌一種名為''atracotoxin''的徑路阻斷劑，對於人類和其他[[靈長目|靈長目]]來說這種毒素有致命威脅。但很少影響除此之外的其他哺乳動物的神經系統。<ref name=museum /> 迄今為止並沒有雌性悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛的咬傷紀錄，而實際上雄性悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛的毒性相較雌性來說至少强五倍，这和其他蜘蛛相反。<ref name=unisydney /><ref name=bitestudy />

在嚴重咬傷時，中毒症狀在一小時內就會出現，平均時間約為28分鐘。兒童發作更快，而事實上有42%的悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛咬傷都發生在兒童身上。<ref name=bitestudy /> 此外其至少有一例兒童死亡案例，這名兒童在被咬傷后15分鐘內死去。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.abc.net.au/7.30/stories/s25168.htm | title=Battling illness, Sutherland still works to save lives from stings and bites | publisher=ABC | date=1999-05-13 | accessdate=23 October 2011 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20121231065530/http://www.abc.net.au/7.30/stories/s25168.htm | archive-date=2012-12-31 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

===抗毒血清===

悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛的抗毒血清由[[墨爾本|墨爾本]][[英聯邦血清實驗室|英聯邦血清實驗室]]的Struan Sutherland領導的團隊發明。<ref name="sutherland">{{cite news|url=https://www.mja.com.au/journal/2002/177/3/struan-keith-sutherlandao-mb-bs-md-dsc-fracp-frcpa|title=Obituary: Struan Keith SutherlandAO MB BS MD DSc FRACP FRCPA|publisher=[[The_Medical_Journal_of_Australia|The Medical Journal of Australia]]|date=January 2002|accessdate=4 September 2012|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209034702/https://www.mja.com.au/journal/2002/177/3/struan-keith-sutherlandao-mb-bs-md-dsc-fracp-frcpa|dead-url=no}}</ref> 自1981年其抗毒血清應用以來，<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=7321948 |year=1981 |last1=Fisher |first1=MM |last2=Raftos |first2=J |last3=McGuinness |first3=RT |last4=Dicks |first4=IT |last5=Wong |first5=JS |last6=Burgess |first6=KR |last7=Sutherland |first7=SK |title=Funnel-web spider (Atrax robustus) antivenom. 2. Early clinical experience |volume=2 |issue=10 |pages=525–6 |journal=The Medical journal of Australia}}</ref> 再沒有人死於悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛的咬傷。<ref name=museum>[http://australianmuseum.net.au/Funnel-web-Spiders-Group Funnel-web Spiders] {{Wayback|url=http://australianmuseum.net.au/Funnel-web-Spiders-Group |date=20120214131031 }}, ''Australian Museum'', Sydney. Retrieved 18 December 2011.</ref><ref name=bitestudy>{{cite journal |pmid=15850438 |year=2005 |last1=Isbister |first1=GK |last2=Gray |first2=MR |last3=Balit |first3=CR |last4=Raven |first4=RJ |last5=Stokes |first5=BJ |last6=Porges |first6=K |last7=Tankel |first7=AS |last8=Turner |first8=E |last9=White |first9=J |last10=Fisher |first10=MM |title=Funnel-web spider bite: A systematic review of recorded clinical cases |volume=182 |issue=8 |pages=407–11 |journal=The Medical journal of Australia}}</ref>

===症狀===
被悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛咬上最初會有劇痛，體表會留下清晰的咬傷痕跡。{{sfn|White|2013|p=190}}<ref name="lancet">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(10)62230-1 |title=Spider bite |year=2011 |last1=Isbister |first1=Geoffrey K |last2=Fan |first2=Hui Wen |journal=The Lancet |volume=378 |issue=9808 |pages=2039}}</ref> 有時若不強行扯掉，悉尼漏斗網蜘蛛並不會鬆口。咬傷后一次需注射兩瓶計量的抗毒血清，每15分鐘一次直到症狀消除。{{sfn|White|2013|p=182}}

